{"tid":1630912,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網片傳防暴警拳打腳踢一被制服黑衣男 暫未獲警方回覆","createTime":"2019-10-06T14:05:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T12:43:31.000Z","uid":212626,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e73b9984d017bc69db5054c36c408cda746201c6","tid":1630912,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:05:29.000Z","msg":"《禁蒙面法》生效第二天，網民號召今午（6日）於港島及九龍遊行，沒申請警方不反對通知書；防暴警察在多區採取驅散及拘捕行動。民陣副召集人陳皓桓在facebook上載片段，顯示有兩名防暴警察對一名已被制服的黑衣男子拳打腳踢。<br />\n<br />\n片段中，有身處較高位置的人見狀，向警方投擲杯裝飲品，又聽到有人大叫「喂，唔好打人啊」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民指出，涉事位置為新蒲崗譽．港灣附近。明報網站正就事件詳情向警方查詢，暫未獲回覆。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191006/s00001/1570363670065/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191006%2Fs00001%2F1570363670065%2F&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6gx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=d539ccf0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191006%2Fs00001%2F1570363670065%2F&h=091d1943\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191006/s00001/1570363670065/</a>"},{"pid":"9eb51cf638c3d23caf3e17c7c6e2cca6e977a64c","tid":1630912,"uid":159762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:06:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港警察濫權實錄資料庫</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fpolice-timeline&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6gx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=36a24809\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有英文同日文版 大家落力share俾更多外國人睇！！</span>"},{"pid":"4511cd61cd180645e47cb9c2376cfe6e18c8603d","tid":1630912,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:06:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/figochanhw/videos/604112270125054/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffigochanhw%2Fvideos%2F604112270125054%2F&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6gx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=ff1e59e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/figochanhw/videos/604112270125054/</a>"},{"pid":"ee2c560d736f1e04615a36e707e4676e45977e9a","tid":1630912,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b139ae0d294c8bef966fe6194d7f6e73b8b9589","tid":1630912,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:27:45.000Z","msg":"警察會話要調查拍攝者，然後告投擲杯裝飲品的人襲警"},{"pid":"021f8db68a96bfaeae0001358b3e271377b7a8b6","tid":1630912,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:42:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bece2b083217c604c2a6a9585812b5cab7e9111","tid":1630912,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"386de082f57079e49a710365b7c69798ce062d75","tid":1630912,"uid":251083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:13:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9cafd651c6b4c3393a9ace32b23cf0b61f02cae","tid":1630912,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:16:33.000Z","msg":"驚慌: 暴徒扮成驚賊 對政見不同人士拳打腳踢 我地驚慌強烈譴責暴徒行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12104fdd3e392fdad3e3bc5e051f4e0395efbb95","tid":1630912,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:18:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JG49P0v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJG49P0v.jpg&h=bfdca82e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行動Post : <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634329\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634329</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">目標一、哂馬</span></strong></span><br />\n由於警狗唔再批不反，即使批左亦會製造衝突。<br />\n為左令和理非可以舒舒服服地出返黎，展示人數同民意，<br />\n所以就利用黃店門外既人龍，製造畫面同話題吸引媒體注意。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">目標二、支持黃色經濟</span></span></strong><br />\n依幾個月生意難免受影響，加上可能被藍絲杯葛，<br />\n良心黃店係好需要大家支持。<br />\n最實際既支持當然就係拎銀包出黎，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>入錢入錢入錢！</strong></span><br />\n另外參考連登既食評，由於良心經營既關係，黃店食物質素一般都偏高，<br />\n絕對係win win雙贏！<br />\n<br />\n------------國際文宣------------<br />\n請將買返黎既貨物/食物/單據同排隊盛況<br />\n一齊用<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">#Buy4HK</span></span></strong><br />\n放上IG, Twitter, reddit"},{"pid":"1c9840be479684290f72201902107a82ea2096e8","tid":1630912,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:23:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70771ea83b4989494e36eaa641f8d7db9b21e39e","tid":1630912,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:42:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6b293c6f703a603699d1d39b88ba9b1aad52a2","tid":1630912,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}